      <title>How to shred (permanently delete) files from your Hard Disks on Ubuntu Linux</title>
      <link>http://galigio.org/2012/02/28/how-to-shred-permanently-delete-files-from-your-hard-disks-on-ubuntu-linux/</link>
      <comments>http://galigio.org/2012/02/28/how-to-shred-permanently-delete-files-from-your-hard-disks-on-ubuntu-linux/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Feb 2012 02:21:38 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>galigio</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Computers & Internet]]></category>
